        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">If you look at where ex-BuzzFeed people tend to end up, i.e. the world&#39;s leading media companies, it might be that they understand digital culture better than the people making the same &quot;listicle&quot; joke.</p>&mdash; Patrick Smith (@psmith) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/psmith/status/1260816435829444609?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 14, 2020</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
        "metadata": {
